data.title: Aryan Khan Bail Rejected: Twitterati Comes Out in Support of Shah Rukh Khan’s Son, Shows Displeasure at NDPS Court’s Decision
data.meta_description: After Aryan Khan's bail has been rejected by the special NDPS court, he will have to spend another night in custody. His lawyers have moved to Bombay High Court seeking bail and the matter will be heard on October 21.
